'''Austin Glacier''' ({{Coord|54|4|S|37|12|W|type:glacier_source:GNIS|display=inline,title}}) is a [[glacier]] flowing north to [[Beckmann Fjord]], [[Bay of Isles]], on the north coast of [[South Georgia Island|South Georgia]]. The name appears to be first used on a 1931 [[British Admiralty]] chart.
